## ğŸ“Œ Procedure (Key Steps)
Here, for demonstration purposes, we are performing a file transfer attack as an attacker. Later we will create a OS disk snapshot of the affected VM in Azure, copy the snapshot to an Azure file share stored under a different resource group, mount the file share containing the snapshot directly onto the forensic workstation, and then export the injected malicious file using Autopsy. We will then upload it to VirusTotal website for analysis.


